<br>
&quot;Samos...well...it's empty.  It's slightly hard getting a tribe off, which I am sure you know.  I hope you'll be able to drop by again.&quot;<br>
<br>
She eyed Yakut down once more before she brought the shamaness into an embrace.  Amarice lowered her voice and this time as she whispered to Yakut, her voice was full of sincerety instead of sarcasm.<br>
